CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 21, reads: "6. General's tubeless whitewall tire winners, Doris Bell, Mrs. M.B. Hooper and Beatrice Dright, flanked by Campbell General Tire and Hawkinson Treads salesman"
TitMainTitle: Whitewall tire winners, Doris Bell, Mrs. M.B. Hooper, and Beatrice Dright, flanked by four men, including Bill Carter, Harry Walker, Henry Ford on right, and Frank H. Lavelle, posed in Hawkinson Treads, Inc. and Campbell General Tire Co. booth in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
